---
title: Veggie Pad See Ew with Bok Choy, Mushrooms and Peanuts
description: Pad See Ew—one of the most popular Thai noodle dishes—uses wide rice noodles to soak up its sweet soy-based sauce! Flavoured with ginger, garlic, and Thai basil, this stir-fry packs some yummy flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-pad-see-ew-460acd1a.jpg
